{"blogid": "124021711", "writerAge": "码龄2年", "writerBlogNum": "22", "writerCollect": "49", "writerComment": "6", "writerFan": "9", "writerGrade": "2级", "writerIntegral": "235", "writerName": "Adair～Z", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124021711.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "82385", "writerRankWeekly": "516791", "writerThumb": "8", "writerVisitNum": "34685", "blog_read_count": "796", "blog_time": "于 2022-04-07 17:21:57 发布", "blog_title": "WordPress网站如何更新PHP版本", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>导读：</p>\n<p>参考链接：<a class=\"has-card\" href=\"https://tuyogf.top/wordpress%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0php%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC.html\" title=\"WordPress网站如何更新PHP版本 – Rookie diary (tuyogf.top)\"><span class=\"link-card-box\"><span class=\"link-title\">WordPress网站如何更新PHP版本 – Rookie diary (tuyogf.top)</span><span class=\"link-link\"><img alt=\"icon-default.png?t=M276\" class=\"link-link-icon\" src=\"image\\icon-default.png\"/>https://tuyogf.top/wordpress%e7%bd%91%e7%ab%99%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e6%9b%b4%e6%96%b0php%e7%89%88%e6%9c%ac.html</span></span></a></p> 当WORDPRESS 网站在管理后台显示您的站点正在运行不安全的PHP版本（7.2.33），应当进行更新。此时我们需要根据自己的需求进行更新。\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"问题描述\">问题描述：</h2>\n<p>在WordPress后台页面显示需要更新PHP版本，版本过低不安全。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\cc1f9d017a35d4e4cb3f7b63d5e2dcfa.png\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"解决方案\">解决方案：</h2>\n<p>思路：安装新版本PHP代码，安装后进行版本切换。</p>\n<p>采用简单的方案步骤如下：</p>\n<p>使用宝塔面板进行操作：</p>\n<p>在宝塔面板上找到软件商店，选择运行环境，找到比较新的PHP版本安装即可。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\e78bb374e90ca9ff6166f477224f833d.png\"/></p>\n<p>然后在宝塔面板找到网站管理页面。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\28c0b5fd3107e0fd0731009c0e3b67df.png\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>找到需要的网站，找到设置进行点击。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\93dc6abec79edd6564c21a0636059b54.png\"/></p>\n<p>点击PHP版本，找到更高版本PHP点击切换即可。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"image\\fd44230266ae4043bf6b68b4c2a0fef7.png\"/></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}